<html>
  <h1>Your Paddlefest volunteer confirmation</h1>
  <p>
    Thank you for registering to be a volunteer for Paddlefest! Our event could
    not possibly happen without volunteers like you! We are looking forward to
    seeing you at the event!
  </p>
  <p>
    We will get in contact with you with more information about the event if
    necessary, but if necessary, please reach out to us at
    <a href="mailto:info@ohioriverpaddlefest.org"
      >info@ohioriverpaddlefest.org</a
    >!
  </p>
  <p>For your records, here is a copy of your information:</p>
  <table>
    <tr>
      <td>Name</td>
      <td><%= data.name %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Email</td>
      <td><%= data.email %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Phone</td>
      <td><%= data.phonenum %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Shirt Size</td>
      <td><%= data.shirt_size %></td>
    </tr>
  </table>
  <p>And here are your shifts:</p>
  <pre><%- jobs.replace(/\n/g, '<br />') %></pre>
  <p>
    If anything goes wrong on our end, we may ask for your Volunteer ID number:
    <%= id %>
  </p>
  <br />
  <p>
    Again, thank you for volunteering for Paddlefest! We are looking forward to
    working with you, and if you need us in the meantime or need to change your
    volunteer signup, please don't hesitate to reach out.
  </p>
  <p>- The Paddlefest volunteer committee</p>
</html>
